      <interpParagraph label="1003-2-g-Interp-2" marker="2.">
        <title>Adjustment of exemption threshold for depository institutions.</title>
        <content>For data collection in 2013, the asset-size exemption threshold is $42 million. Banks, savings associations, and credit unions with assets at or below $42 million as of December 31, 2013, are exempt from collecting data for 2013.</content>
